Jewelry Care: Protect jewelry from from scratching, banging, extreme temperatures, strenuous activity, intense sunlight and chemicals (swimming pools & hot tubs). It is not recommended to wear jewelry in the shower. Wipe your jewelry off with a soft cloth after you wear it – this will keep jewelry clean of make up and skin oils. Store jewelry separately in a reclosable plastic bag or box. Apply makeup and hairspray before putting on your jewelry. Makeup and hairspray contain chemicals that may affect your jewelry.​
